<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2588453>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Complete specimens of species of genera Lucilina, Onithochiton and Acanthopleura: A. Lucilina lamellosa forma typica, Xisha Islands, 58M-1246, BL 28.0 mm; B. Lucilina lamellosa forma costata, Hainan Island, 55-640, BL 21.0 mm; C. Lucilina tenuicostata, Hainan Island, stn 13, BL 10.0 mm; D. Onithochiton cf. hirasei, Guangdong Province, BL 29.0 mm; E. Onithochiton stracki, Guangdong Province, BL 19.0 mm; F. Acanthopleura loochooana, Hainan, stn 28, BL 26.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2588453/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2588457>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Lucilina lamellosa forma typica, South China Sea, 18°39’N, 111°40’E, BL 15.0 mm: A. Valve I, dorsal view; B. Valve V, dorsal view; C. Valve VIII, dorsal view; D. Valve V, detail of tegmentum in central area; E. Valve V, rostral view; F. Valve VIII, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2588457/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2588461>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Lucilina lamellosa forma costata, Hainan, Xincun, depth 0.5 m on old corals, 21.04.1958, BL 14.0 mm: A. Valve I, dorsal view; B. Valve II, dorsal view; C. Valve V, dorsal view; D. Valve VIII, dorsal view; E. Valve V, detail of tegmentum in central area; F. Valve V, rostral view; G. Valve VIII, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2588461/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

